    "We now outline the general themes of the Forum discussions for each of the three pillars of MDTs: human immune system biology, the clinic, and mathematical and computational modeling.",
    "And we extract a collection of action items for a 5-year plan to further MDT development.",
    "The human immune system is highly specialized and has evolved to have exquisite specificity for defending its host from injury and infection.",
    "During health, the immune response is tightly orchestrated to respond to threats without inducing significant tissue damage, but dysregulation can occur, contributing to cancer or autoimmunity 14.",
